Release frontend changes to staging; validate UI/filters with stakeholders.

Run controlled backfill on a small historical window; validate results.

Full backfill (if approved) with monitoring and throttling.

Production deploy & monitor health metrics for 48‚Äì72 hours.

Risks & Mitigations
Embedding model version changes ‚Äî Mitigate by recording embedding_model and pipeline_version per row; allow re-compute with a specified version.

High compute cost for embeddings ‚Äî Mitigate via batching, caching embeddings for identical texts, or using lightweight embedding model.

Incomplete Helios / AI text ‚Äî Mark score as not_computed and surface reason in UI.

Interpretability ‚Äî Provide clear docs and examples showing what high/low scores mean.

